                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-218-off1158 t18280221-218-cd1159"></join>, 1 pair of boots, value 2s.6d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280221-218-victim1275" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
